### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Hackathon API Test Suite — REST Client (VS Code)
### Click "Send Request" above any request to test
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

@BASE    = http://localhost:8000
@API_KEY = hackathon-secret-key-123

### ── System ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{BASE}}/health

### Swagger Docs (open in browser)
# GET {{BASE}}/docs

### ── AI Endpoints ────────────────────────────────────

### Chat — with domain context
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/chat
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Show me all offline devices and explain possible reasons",
  "include_context": true
}

###

### Chat — without context (pure LLM)
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/chat
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "What is MQTT protocol?",
  "include_context": false
}

###

### Feedback — thumbs up
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/feedback
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "response_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID",
  "rating": 1
}

###

### Feedback — thumbs down
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/feedback
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "response_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID",
  "rating": -1
}

###

### Translate
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/translate
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Device is offline. Check network connection.",
  "target_lang": "hi-IN"
}

### ── Data Endpoints ───────────────────────────────────

### List all entities
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/entities
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Get entity by ID
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/entities/dev_001
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Filter by status
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/entities/status/offline
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Get alerts
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/alerts
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Chat history
GET {{BASE}}/api/data/history
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

### ── Sarvam Direct (test your API key) ───────────────

### Direct Sarvam Chat (bypass your app)
POST https://api.sarvam.ai/v1/chat/completions
api-subscription-key: YOUR_SARVAM_KEY_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "sarvam-2b",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Hello, what can you do?"}
  ]
}

### ── RAG Endpoints ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### RAG Status
GET {{BASE}}/api/rag/status
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Toggle RAG on/off
POST {{BASE}}/api/rag/toggle
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Upload a document
POST {{BASE}}/api/rag/upload
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "IoT Troubleshooting Guide",
  "content": "When a device goes offline, first check the network connection. For MQTT devices, verify the broker is running and the client ID is unique. For CoAP devices, check the UDP port 5683 is open. For LwM2M devices, ensure the bootstrap server is reachable. Common issues include: firewall blocking ports, expired certificates, and duplicate client IDs causing disconnections."
}

###

### List RAG documents
GET {{BASE}}/api/rag/documents
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Delete a RAG document
DELETE {{BASE}}/api/rag/documents/REPLACE_WITH_DOC_ID
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}

###

### Chat WITH RAG enabled
POST {{BASE}}/api/ai/chat
X-API-Key: {{API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "How do I fix an offline MQTT device?",
  "include_context": true,
  "use_rag": true
}
